divs: sighting detailsi got an olympus e-510 for a gift and started to take pictures of everything, and then forgot that i had taken some weird pictures. i just went through the memory card and found several things. any explanations are appreciated, because i'm not knowledgeable about the ufo thing, but i can't explain these either. the first pictures were taken at 9:52 - 9:54 on february 20, 2008. i was on my way to bed and saw lights and snapped through the upstairs bedroom window. these are yellow\gold shape changing things. then i went downstairs and onto my deck and took the next three pictures - one of a disc (moon?) against a lighter sky, and then two pictures of curtains or garments or lace, except that i cannot find anything in my house that would have gotten in the way of the pictures. are these tracks of something? this happened the same night about 5 minutes after the above pictures were taken. june 28, 2008, i took 2 pictures of something, in the evening i believe, which must be the moon with light arcing over it. finally, i am sending three pictures of v-shaped contrails which i am sure are normal, but i can't figure out if the planes started at the same spot or ended at the same spot! these are morning pictures, taken from my deck.
